    <note>Fan(2) Xiang(2) [571] He was a fiscal expert (xiaoda caili). Fan(2) Yu(5)'s [591] father. XCB, 105.10a-11a, 171.16b, 174.12b-13a, 187.15a, 192.5b, 13a; SS, 303.16b-17b. Xiang(2)'s granddaughter, wife of Li(2) Fu (8)[19329] (q.v.), is listed as a Changan resident and he may have moved to the former Tang capital, but I am only going to move Xiang(2)'s son, Bao [19326] (Li(2) Fu(8)'s father-in-law) to Changan. There is no doubt about identification of Bao as Li(2) Fu(8)'s grandfather-in-law since both Bao have the same posthumous title. CBD, 2, 1629.</note>
